---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import Skillbox from '@/components/astroComponents/Skillbox.astro';
import HeadingLine from '@/components/astroComponents/HeadingLine.astro';
---

<Layout title="Synchat | Snehan Chakra Varthi">
	<div
		class="mb-20 flex max-w-5xl flex-col items-center space-y-8 px-4 text-center font-redhat text-sm dark:text-pink-600 sm:px-8 sm:text-base md:px-12"
	>
		<h1
			class="dark:text-shadow-3d-dark text-shadow mt-14 font-microgammaBold text-3xl text-cyan-400 dark:text-white sm:text-5xl"
		>
			SYNCHAT
		</h1>

		<HeadingLine title="what is it?" />
		<p>
			Synchat is an under-development side project. It is a set of server functions that are webhook
			listening APIs written in <Skillbox skill="flask" iconClass="i-skill-icons-flask-light " />, <Skillbox
				skill="python"
			/> and <Skillbox
				skill="express"
				iconClass="dark:i-skill-icons-expressjs-light i-skill-icons-expressjs-dark "
			/>, <Skillbox skill="nodejs" iconClass="i-logos-nodejs-icon " />. Each of them are
			containerised using <Skillbox skill="docker" iconClass="i-skill-icons-docker " /> and they use
			<span class="text-decoration">Meta Whatsapp Business API</span> to leverage Whatsapp to provide
			a seamless AI utilities service through voice messages.
		</p>

		<p>For more info check out my github</p>
		<a href=""></a>
	</div>
</Layout>
